		<title>Persistence and Resistance</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/PathwayToHappiness/~3/DdL8taxPOPc/</link>
		<comments>http://www.pathwaytohappiness.com/journal/2012/05/21/persistence-and-resistance/#comments</comments>
