		<description><![CDATA[Understanding how your mind creates emotional reactions is key to making personal change.  This understanding of the mind is done through mindfulness, also know as Self Awareness.  In a basic level of awareness you might notice how someone&#8217;s mood changes.  A deeper level of awareness allows you notice your own mood, and how it affects [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Understanding how your mind creates emotional reactions is key to making personal change.  This understanding of the mind is done through mindfulness, also know as Self Awareness.  In a basic level of awareness you might notice how someone&#8217;s mood changes.  A deeper level of awareness allows you notice your own mood, and how it affects your behavior and interactions.  A deeper level of awareness will allow you to perceive the factors affecting your mood and change them.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://pathwaytohappiness.com/podcast/pod41-self-awareness.mp3">Self Awareness and Mindfulness </a>   Podcast #41    38 Min</strong></p>
<p>Self Awareness, also called Mindfulness, is an important step to permanently changing your negative thoughts, emotional reactions, and self destructive behaviors.</p>
<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/PathwayToHappiness/~4/CTAmwiR2Z8s" height="1" width="1"/>]]></content:encoded>
