			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I don&#8217;t think we should just manage our anger.  I believe in eliminating anger.  Trying to control triggers, circumstances, and other people so we don&#8217;t become angry is too much work. It is much easier to identify and change the core beliefs causing our anger.  In this free audio podcast I outline what the process of managing and eliminating anger looks like when you do it with awareness.</p>
