			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Faith is more than a set of beliefs there is no evidence for or a doctrine of religious beliefs.  Faith is a force.  It is an aspect of your personal will power that you can use in various ways.  One way to use the power of your faith is to invest it in conceptual ideas.  In don Miguel Ruiz&#8217;s book The Fifth Agreement he outlines a more impeccable use of the power of your faith.</p>
<p><strong><a title="Faith" href="http://pathwaytohappiness.com/podcast/pod30-Faith-Knowledge.mp3">Faith:  What You Don&#8217;t Know   (26min) </a></strong></p>
<p>We&#8217;ll be delving deeper into the insights in don Miguel Ruiz&#8217;s new book, The Fifth Agreement, in future audios.   I think this one help fills in some gaps about the concept of faith and perhaps makes it a little less abstract.</p>
