		<title>Don’t Take Anything Personally</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/PathwayToHappiness/~3/cSCYvZYLlng/</link>
		<comments>http://www.pathwaytohappiness.com/journal/2007/02/23/dont-take-anything-personally/#comments</comments>
